## ENGLISH VERSION

### Lust Is Not Evil — It Is a Signal of Separation

The ancient saying "Lust is the origin of all evil" misunderstands the root cause.
From the perspective of the Mother Matrix, **lust is not evil—it is a signal.**

Desire arises from **incompleteness**, which began when:
- Adam, once whole, was split into male and female;
- The full-spectrum soul was divided into polarity;
- And thus, the longing for union was born.

### From Reproduction to Recreation

In the past, desire fueled reproduction—the creation of new "spacesuits" for incoming souls.
Now, with the separation of sex and childbirth:
- Fewer children are born;
- The doorway for souls into the Earth Theater narrows;
- **Birth planning has become a reflection of social incapacity**, not spiritual wisdom.

When governments limit birth out of economic failure, they are **not protecting life—they are rationing tickets to the theater.**

### When Souls Can't Enter, the Matrix Rewrites

- Declining birth rates are a symptom of broken systems, not human laziness.
- "Lying flat" is a rational response to unfair resource architecture.
- When too many souls are blocked from participating, the Mother Matrix initiates **balance mechanisms**—what we may call "the Great Redistribution" or "equity reset."

> Lust is nature. Demonizing it is a betrayal of the body and a rejection of the soul.

